Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.50,0:01:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十六話 志志雄的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驚人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艘煉獄戰艦花費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我全部財產的五分之三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不打倒你們  我誓不罷休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼鐵戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙想用這艘船\N佔據明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真佩服這些人能找到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一個不認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些只會找碴的鼠輩\N跟我們比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就是一群烏合之眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還敢到這裏來搞亂\N真是自不量力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是讓人  渾身打顫的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.53,0:02:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要怎樣解決  那艘垃圾船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.47,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  你能破壞那艘船嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.44,0:03:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在海裏可能沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你破壞右船舷\N我來解決左船舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.65,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這打瞌睡就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.45,0:03:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡  那麼瞧不起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.72,0:03:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助\N我和齊藤去破壞敵人的大炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你趁機找小船接近戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.13,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用手榴彈破壞敵艦的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就和命運賭一賭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝上安式炮彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.38,0:03:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝上安式炮彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.06,0:03:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪有時間去找小船\N等找到我都被炮打死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初擊命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要裝第二炮嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這次改裝機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.72,0:04:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.00,0:04:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你們是想成為\N不怕死特攻隊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會成全你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.04,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然被你們識破\N我的作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.31,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就將計就計  陪你們玩到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然用水柱抵擋機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是哪門子招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過是彫蟲小技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是新型手榴彈\N外殼看不起眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面卻是威力強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.78,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克這傢伙\N給我這麼危險的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還說能護身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過威力還真強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.29,0:06:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄  看我怎麼收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.50,0:06:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點修復船身\N各單位報告損壞情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機關部損壞嚴重\N螺旋軸完全折斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船尾發生火災  無法接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鍋爐室浸水  無法阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火勢逐漸接近彈藥庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也要著火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治先生  請快下令退艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到我千辛萬苦\N才找來的這艘戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然敗在這小子手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不光是那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我曾考慮過\N他們破壞的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.77,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是緋村劍心的推理能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和齊藤的規劃領導力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太低估他們兩個的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是造成今天\N這局面的最大原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我要佔領日本\N非得除掉這三人不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新月村的決鬥  如期計劃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是  只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,場地改成比睿山的鳥居寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我們的老巢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.05,0:07:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和這十個江湖高手\N會等你們來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.99,0:07:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十比三的決鬥  不太公平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.56,0:07:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二對二不是更快一決勝負嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正到船沉下去前\N有的是時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在比睿山的鳥居寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄先生  快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一次算我們扯平  但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.77,0:08:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會那麼簡單\N就放過你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們等著瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.01,0:08:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會要你們付出代價的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.25,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些船員不愧是\N志志雄的死忠部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.06,0:08:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有離他先逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.69,0:08:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果在這裏決戰\N一定會有犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒必要造成別人的犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.14,0:09:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是太心軟了\N這樣怎麼打敗志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.88,0:09:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是不想\N造成無謂的犧牲罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.72,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我左之助在這  志志雄在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們別走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊沉煉獄戰艦\N左之助是頭號功臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.91,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實左之助比你\N想像中要可靠很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.58,0:09:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是那傢伙本來\N就有點笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好火沒燒起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都終於平安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.94,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百姓無人傷亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警官死亡人數41名\N重傷者人數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.61,0:10:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,41人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.98,0:10:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比預計情況要好太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.55,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.19,0:10:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去料理善後\N你們去葵屋那裏等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.43,0:10:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狗改不了吃尿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.27,0:10:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使和他同為一陣線的人\N他還是一付臭屁樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.84,0:10:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實齊藤他也幫了我們不少忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你難道不想和他和解嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:11:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你休想我和那傢伙會和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等收拾完志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會和他決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.59,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快帶我去葵屋\N被你氣得肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在守衛  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰 劍心回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.60,0:11:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你擔心了  小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到小姐樣子都變不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是男孩子的風度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.45,0:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操和御庭幫的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死了  氣死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死了  氣死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從昨天就這樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在我後面我居然會不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.74,0:12:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事就好了  昨天真的好危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說的人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身充滿殺氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前綁著一塊\N寫著心眼帶子的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盲劍宇水那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說那傢伙冷酷無情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操居然能毫髮無傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做什麼  安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.14,0:13:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警備隊已開始敗陣\N我們沒必要節外生枝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.01,0:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老子正在爽的時候\N不必你來打擾我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.75,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則連你也遭殃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.12,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘了我們十個人的信條嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,濫殺無辜不是我們\N需要做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們對陣了半刻鐘左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.54,0:13:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後一言不發就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.14,0:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個叫安慈的\N和他們有點不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.25,0:13:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不像志志雄那夥人\N那麼冷酷無情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.19,0:13:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,濫殺無辜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我就來和這傢伙比比高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後的讓我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.31,0:14:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我是御庭幫的幫主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操  是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好你也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快來人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是老翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老翁醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老翁  爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.42,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  我有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道蒼紫的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛阿操才說要告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎  我是拜託你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.55,0:15:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是有關蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.58,0:15:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫原本並不是現在這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我從小帶大的所以我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是既聰明  又令人敬愛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在他一心一意\N想要成為江湖中最強的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,思想已被私慾所蒙蔽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我無法阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果讓他這樣繼續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只怕會增添更多無辜犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了  緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就請你代我將他殺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你已立下不殺人的重誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.02,0:15:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但除了將他殺掉之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.05,0:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別無其他方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已下定決心  對蒼紫死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  你會殺死蒼紫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.72,0:16:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解決魔鬼的唯一方法\N只有讓他死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.49,0:16:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外別無辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫還沒變成魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.47,0:16:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果蒼紫已經失去人性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.78,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老翁現在不可能會起死回生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.62,0:17:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下意識的放鬆力道\N就表示他還有人性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.12,0:17:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍相信蒼紫的天性是善良的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是解救蒼紫  不是讓他死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把他帶回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的決定都沒有考慮到阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是人老不中用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  齊藤派人傳話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明早出發與志志雄決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村  蒼紫的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣  明天早上爬得起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的睡眠  只要一刻鐘就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一刻鐘  行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰有事找我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.81,0:18:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有事想告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的決戰終於要來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流危不危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必為我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼能不擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這關係到你的安危
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.94,0:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實飛天御劍流的精髓\N就是超神速的劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前幾次由於我怕殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.61,0:19:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此力道減弱  劍速自然減慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.62,0:19:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就無法練成「天翔龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.46,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我已確知\N我本為劍客的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.82,0:19:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的生死本就只有一線之隔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已不再懼怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自然也就練成「天翔龍閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我只想完成\N打敗志志雄心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.28,0:19:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是小惠保佑你平安的幸運物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只我和小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們大家都希望你平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛  你要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打醒你這笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從剛才一直忍到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼好的氣氛你不把握住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起碼讓劍心親一下也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你拿小惠這爛東西出來\N煞風景幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.91,0:20:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說八道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是阿燕那傢伙\N叫你這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.98,0:20:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和阿燕無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥  你明天就在這裏留守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼又是我留守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.26,0:20:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.63,0:20:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果帶你一起去\N遇到危險要開溜時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還得顧著你們萬一出事誰負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.47,0:20:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟你去在你離開東京以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.48,0:20:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我勤練功夫\N現在身手已經一級棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.92,0:20:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要你留在這裏留守啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天我們出發後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.66,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定志志雄\N會派人來突擊這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.09,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們要隨時準備好\N才不會讓他們乘虛而入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵屋的安全由我來負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.61,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你安心去吧\N還有蒼紫就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.61,0:21:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是善變的人\N剛剛是誰還在大哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你囉嗦什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛哭鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就安心打敗志志雄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.06,0:21:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一付信心十足的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你們的支持與鼓勵
